claim.claim-text:
1. A server apparatus comprising:
a reception unit which receives print data that comprises print setting information that indicates whether a user is able to execute printing;
a storage unit which stores the print data received by the reception unit;
a list sending unit which sends a list of the print data, which the user who is an operator of an image forming apparatus is able to execute, to the image forming apparatus; and
a transmission unit which transmits the print data selected by the user at an interface of the image forming apparatus from the list of the print data sent by the list sending unit to the image forming apparatus.

15. A method of managing print data, comprising:
receiving the print data that comprises print setting information that indicates whether a user is able to execute printing;
storing the received print data in a storage unit;
sending a list of the print data, which the user who is an operator of an image forming apparatus is able to execute, to the image forming apparatus; and
transmitting, to the image forming apparatus, the print data selected by the user at an interface of the image forming apparatus from the list of the print data sent to the image forming apparatus.
